{"tid":60012,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"周融：幫港出聲facebook用戶群僅次100毛","createTime":"2016-12-30T06:12:57.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-30T07:33:38.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8176187d874c3ff229412bcb916aa1aa982e3389","tid":60012,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T06:12:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161230/large/1483076463_ef8f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161230%2Flarge%2F1483076463_ef8f.jpg&h=e5627438&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早前獲人大委員長張德江接見的「幫港出聲」召集人周融，在《紫荊雜誌》撰文，吹噓「幫港出聲」的facebook專頁人數不是很多，「但根據面書2016年11月專頁其中一周的互動情況的公開數據，幫港出聲面書專頁的用戶群，在香港政治性網媒中佔到第三位。第一是《蘋果日報》，第二是《100毛》，第三就是幫港出聲，第四第五第六分別是港人講地、HKG報和時聞香港」。<br />\n<br />\n當年周融牽頭發起反佔中簽名運動，就聲稱有180多萬人支持，但被揭不仔細檢查簽名人士身份，當中「水份」甚多。周融今次在文中沒有具體列出有關數據，但就以此下結論指「整體來看，網路媒體的佔有率是反對派六建制派四」。他稱2013年前，網路媒體的佔有率差不多是反對派全取，「按照前後這個比例對比，建制派網上發聲有很大進步」。<br />\n<br />\n他又讚自己的「HKG報」fb和「幫港出聲」fb互相輝映，「在網絡方面，建制派應該多一點強一點，多多益善」。<br />\n<br />\n2016年12月30日下午1時30分各fb專頁真實數據：<br />\n《蘋果日報》粉絲總人數1,912,527共2,009,276個讚好 / 本周新的讚好4,603(跌8.1%) <br />\n《100毛》粉絲總人數1,016,492共1,040,919個讚好 / 本周新的讚好2,455(升6.4%)<br />\n「港人講地」粉絲總人數274,666共294,679個讚好 / 本周新的讚好765(升1.2%) <br />\n「時聞香港」粉絲總人數196,047共214,221個讚好 / 本周新的讚好366(升5.5%) <br />\n「幫港出聲」粉絲總人數141,992共154,829個讚好 / 本周新的讚好377(跌33.4%)<br />\n「HKG報」粉絲總人數70,390共72,898個讚好 / 本周新的讚好411(跌9.9%)"},{"pid":"8f640dee42822e9c9521c8170e14505e7a0ba0eb","tid":60012,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T06:15:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9bebe8b11f43270e4b2cf86c121da1d059d6ada7","tid":60012,"uid":47558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T06:18:10.000Z","msg":"讀到大學未呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c12bcfdc2eba0153f5300251decfec48e7de152","tid":60012,"uid":64225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T06:45:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>讀到大學未呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一陣中七仔又嬲嬲豬"},{"pid":"3bb44af7864ab7775936cfbab8a47bf6e95865d0","tid":60012,"uid":48358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T06:48:39.000Z","msg":"蚛蝈人用微信啦用咩Facebook呀"},{"pid":"9800c1cba3bd7852eda0aea93270c67f1568f07d","tid":60012,"uid":5715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T06:49:03.000Z","msg":"佢個樣好似講緊：吹吖，吹大啲吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2b6412eb611d62a1c7c48acade7627d75ca18d4","tid":60012,"uid":42550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T06:50:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢個樣好似講緊：吹吖，吹大啲吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n乜唔係wfc咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f9b9ebd0b2113d7718d02957ef3f22b0473af1f","tid":60012,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T06:51:12.000Z","msg":"好多南美人like<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef61345c87f112282d87f78e87342c9776f70a5b","tid":60012,"uid":6275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T06:51:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/30/145123_49dfa18a4776cd2448fbcf0a0caa10ba.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F30%2F145123_49dfa18a4776cd2448fbcf0a0caa10ba.jpg&h=bb97ea5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb58509d8eb3397761de8d9581552e30fdc16779","tid":60012,"uid":10290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor